                "abstract": [
                    {
                        "value": "Herman Singer (1915-2001) was an editor of the \u003cspan class=\"ead-emph ead-emph-italic\"\u003eNew Leader\u003c/span\u003e from 1945-1950. He worked for Radio Free Europe (RFE) and collected documents relating to his work on Calverton, Socialist Party history, NY Call/SDF, the Newspaper Guild-Free Europe Unit, and \u003cspan class=\"ead-emph ead-emph-italic\"\u003eFree Europe Guild News\u003c/span\u003e. He corresponded regularly with  Bob Rindel, Sam Solon, Tom Berger, Calverton and other editors and publishers.",
